tooltips.Realized PnL: Total profit and loss from closed trades. Formula: (Trade PnL).
tooltips.ROI: Return on Investment: percentage gain or loss on starting funds. Formula: (PnL / Starting Funds) * 100.
tooltips.Sharpe ratio: Risk-adjusted return using total volatility. Formula: (Average Return - Risk-Free Rate) / Standard Deviation of Returns. Uses a risk-free rate of 3.
tooltips.Sortino ratio: Risk-adjusted return using downside risk. Formula: (Average Return - Risk-Free Rate) / Downside Deviation. Uses a risk-free rate of 3.
tooltips.Realized Profit: Total profit from all profitable trades. Formula: (Profitable Trade PnL).
tooltips.Realized Loss: Total loss from all losing trades. Formula: (Losing Trade PnL).
tooltips.Average pnl %: Average percentage profit or loss per trade. Formula: (Trade PnL %) / Number of Trades.
tooltips.Average profit %: Average percentage gain per profitable trade. Formula: (Profitable Trade PnL %) / Number of Profitable Trades.
tooltips.Average loss %: Average percentage loss per losing trade. Formula: (Losing Trade PnL %) / Number of Losing Trades.
tooltips.Volume: Total trading volume in base currency. Formula: (Trade Volume).
tooltips.Buy volume: Total volume of buy trades in base currency. Formula: (Buy Trade Volume).
tooltips.Sell volume: Total volume of sell trades in base currency. Formula: (Sell Trade Volume).
tooltips.Buys: Number of buy trades executed. Formula: Count(Buy Trades). Groups trades with identical timestamps.
tooltips.Sells: Number of sell trades executed. Formula: Count(Sell Trades). Groups trades with identical timestamps.
tooltips.Trades with profit: Number of trades resulting in profit. Formula: Count(Profitable Trades). Groups trades with identical timestamps.
tooltips.Trades with loss: Number of trades resulting in loss. Formula: Count(Losing Trades). Groups trades with identical timestamps.
tooltips.Fees paid: Total trading fees paid. Formula: (Trade Fees).
